---
supersigil:
  id: optional-tasks/tasks
  type: tasks
  status: draft
title: "Optional Tasks"
---

```supersigil-xml
<Task id="task-1" status="done">
  Required task

  - Do the required work

  <Task id="task-1-1" status="done">
    Required sub-task

    - Sub-task description
  </Task>

  <Task id="task-1-2" status="done" depends="task-1-1">
    Optional sub-task

    - This sub-task is optional
  </Task>
</Task>
```

```supersigil-xml
<Task id="task-2" status="ready" depends="task-1">
  Optional top-level task

  - This entire task is optional
</Task>
```

> **TODO(supersigil-import):** This task was marked as optional in Kiro; supersigil <Task> has no optional attribute (task: task-1-2)
